import React from 'react'
import {} from "./checkout-form.styles";
const CheckoutForm = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormInline>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label>First Name<Required>*</Required></Label>
          <Input />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label>Last Name<Required>*</Required></Label>
          <Input />
        </FormGroup>
      </FormInline>
    </Form>
  )
}

export default CheckoutForm
